name: Taster Pack
description: A 25g sample from each of our seven mixtures so you can try them all and see which of them suits you the best. Only one taster pack per person.

name: Powdered Herbs Mix
description: Our carefully crafted mixture of six finely ground herbs. Together they produce a wonderful flavor which can be used freely in any number of dishes. Ingredients: Parsley, Thyme, Oregano, Basil, Coriander Leaves, Rosemary.

name: Powdered Herbs & Spice Mix
description: Our special mixture of fourteen herbs and spices. Use liberally to improve the flavor of any savory dish! Ingredients: Parsley, Thyme, Oregano, Coriander Leaves, Basil, Rosemary, Sweet Paprika, Hot Paprika, Garlic Powder, Cumin, Black Pepper, Coriander Seeds, Cardamom Seeds, Turmeric.

name: Yemenite Spice Mix
description: A medium hot, very tasty blend of spices. Experiment with it in different dishes! Ingredients: Hot Paprika, Garlic Powder, Black Pepper, Cardamom Seeds, Coriander Seeds.

name: Hot Spice Mix
description: Fairly hot, very tasty mixture of spices. Can be used in any dish which needs a balanced flavor with a little heat. Ingredients: Hot Paprika, Sweet Paprika, Garlic Powder, Turmeric, Cardamom Seeds, Cumin, Coriander Seeds, Black Pepper.

name: Spice Mixture for Chicken
description: Whilst this mixture is very suitable for chicken and fish, try it with other dishes too, perhaps in combination with one of our other mixtures. Ingredients: Sweet Paprika, Garlic Powder, Black Pepper, Cumin, Coriander Seeds, Turmeric.

name: Spice Mixture for Meat
description: Although pepper is the predominant flavor of this mixture, the other spices give it a much fuller and rounder flavor. Ingredients: Black Pepper, Garlic Powder, Coriander Seeds, White Pepper, Cardamom Seeds, Cumin.

name: Spice Mixture for Goulash
description: Although this is called Goulash seasoning it can actually be used in many different types of dishes, usually in combination with other spice mixtures. Ingredients: Sweet Paprika, Garlic Powder, Black Pepper.
